    "millsfield:images_texts": [
      "Waterloo Municipal Airport\nWaterloo, lowa\nMID CONTINENT\nTra",
      "DISTRIBUTED BY WATERLOO NEWS AGENCY, WATERLOO, IOWA\nVIEW OF THE FIELD SIDE OF THE NEW\nAIRPORT TERMINAL BUILDING\nWATERLOO, IOWA\nThis building was dedicated in June 1951.\nIt is very modern throughout,\nthe end behind\nthe airplane housing a spacious restaurant.\nWaterloo is served by air by Mid-Continent\nAirlines both North and South and East and\nWest.\nGENUINE CURTEICH.CHICAGO ''C.T. AMERICAN ART'* POST CARD (REG. U.S. PAT. OFF. )\nPOST CARD\n$ 11.53\n275-\nPLACE\nSTAMP\nHERE\nIC454-N\n2015,\n62396"
